sections.text:
44-5255.Standard health benefit plan, defined.

Standard health benefit plan shall mean a health benefit plan regulated by the Department of Insurance.

SourceLaws 1994, LB 1222, § 33;Laws 2009, LB154, § 10;Laws 2017, LB644, § 8.
